May 29/22 great coffee and great service and great price! Especially for seniors! However,  there is no wifi,  as it has been for awhile now.  Too bad,  a friend quit coming because other shops close by do offer it ... Aug 22/22 good prices, great coffee,  great staff. Busy today, 10:30 -11:00 AM, restaurant was 80 % full. BUT, still no wifi.  When I order on the app, I have to use my data, because there is no wifi. WOW Nov 19/22 Wifi is back! Perfect!

Great location to goto the staff are amazing they go far and beyond what they should do for there customers also there menu is exceptional with tones of items to choose from, from burgers and fries to wraps and chicken nuggies but the best part is how quick and great there service is and how fresh the food is from this particular location I will be coming back when Im in the area again forsure I really hope they come out with some more new items soon as I loved there spicy chicken burgers that recently cane out I ate them for 3 days strait to be honest haha anyways 5 stars all around great job McDonalds

Was privileged to witness a young female manager totally kick butt when dealing with a rude and offensive individual. A customer became irrationally upset with the duration hed waited for his order - became verbally abusive towards staff and unnervingly animated.  The manager simply and calmly explained that his language  and behaviour was  unacceptable, that he would be not be served and that he needed to leave. The customer isnt always right and it was terrific to see someone stand up for themselves and their co-workers.
